title: Foo Fighters drummer Taylor Hawkins dead at 50 - The Associated Press - en Español
content: Foo Fighters drummer Taylor Hawkins dead at 50  The Associated Press - en EspañolView Full Coverage on Google News
description: LOS ANGELES (AP) — Taylor Hawkins, for 25 years the drummer for Foo Fighters and best friend of frontman Dave Grohl, has died during a South American tour with the rock band. He was 50.  There were no immediate details on how Hawkins died, although the band said in a statement Friday that his death was a “tragic and untimely loss.”
